---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about MiMaji Foundation's mission to provide clean, safe water access to communities across East Africa. Founded in 2025, we combine technology and community partnerships."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">Our Story</div>
    <h1>About <em>MiMaji Foundation</em></h1>
    <p>A non-profit initiative born from the belief that clean water access is a fundamental human right — not a privilege reserved for the few.</p>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C360,100 720,20 1080,60 C1260,80 1380,50 1440,60 L1440,100 L0,100Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder Story -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Our Origin</div>
      <div class="section-title">Why We Started MiMaji Foundation</div>
      <div class="origin-image fade-in">
        <img
          src="/nairobi-home-family-4-washing-dishes-by-the-sink-urban-homes.png"
          alt="A Nairobi family of four washing dishes by the kitchen sink in their urban home — illustrating the everyday water access challenges MiMaji Foundation works to solve in Kenya"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1200"
          height="600"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about-grid fade-in">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>While building <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji</a> as a water delivery platform in Nairobi, we discovered something troubling: the communities that needed clean water most were paying the highest prices for the worst quality. Residents in informal settlements like Kibera pay up to 10 times more per litre than households in connected, wealthier neighbourhoods.</p>
          <p>This is a market failure — and a human rights issue. The same technology that powers convenient water delivery for paying customers can be adapted to serve communities who have been overlooked: mapping water quality, educating households, and subsidising access for vulnerable populations.</p>
          <p>MiMaji Foundation was established in 2025 as the social impact arm of MiMaji. Headquartered in Nairobi, Kenya, the Foundation bridges the gap between commercial innovation and social responsibility. We are currently in our pilot phase — small, focused, and building.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-values">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">🎯</div>
            <h4>Impact First</h4>
            <p>Every decision is measured by the number of people who gain access to clean water.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
            <h4>Community Partnership</h4>
            <p>We don't impose solutions — we co-create them with the communities we serve.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">📊</div>
            <h4>Data-Driven</h4>
            <p>We use technology and data to identify needs, track progress, and maximise our reach.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">♻️</div>
            <h4>Sustainability</h4>
            <p>Our solutions are designed to be maintained and owned by the communities themselves.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MiMaji Connection -->
  <section class="bg-sand">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">The MiMaji Ecosystem</div>
      <div class="section-title">Foundation + Platform = Greater Impact</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">The MiMaji Foundation and the MiMaji water delivery platform work hand in hand to create a complete water access ecosystem.</div>
      <div class="ecosystem-image fade-in">
        <img
          src="/Kinds-of-water-delivery-in-Nairobi-including-link-to-MiMaji.png"
          alt="The full Nairobi water delivery ecosystem — boda boda riders, NCWSC tankers, handcart vendors, the MiMaji mobile app, and verified MiMaji delivery riders working together to bring clean water to homes"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1200"
          height="500"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="ecosystem-grid fade-in">
        <div class="eco-card">
          <div class="eco-badge">Platform</div>
          <h3><a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji.co.ke</a></h3>
          <p>Kenya's water delivery technology platform connecting consumers to verified, quality water suppliers. Order water, track delivery, and ensure quality — all from your phone.</p>
          <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-dark" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Visit Platform &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-card">
          <div class="eco-badge foundation">Foundation</div>
          <h3>MiMaji Foundation</h3>
          <p>The social impact arm extending clean water access to underserved communities through testing, education, subsidised delivery, and advocacy programs across East Africa.</p>
          <a href="/programs/" class="btn btn-outline-dark" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Our Programs &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Our Journey</div>
      <div class="section-title">Milestones & Roadmap</div>
      <div class="timeline fade-in">
        <div class="timeline-item completed">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
            <h4>MiMaji Platform Launch</h4>
            <p><a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji.co.ke</a> launched as Kenya&rsquo;s water delivery technology platform. Early research surfaced the depth of urban water pricing inequality across Nairobi.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item completed">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2025</div>
            <h4>Foundation Established</h4>
            <p>MiMaji Foundation set up as the social impact arm. Nairobi Water Price Map research completed. Initial team and pilot plan in place.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item active">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2026 &mdash; Now</div>
            <h4>Phase 1 Pilot</h4>
            <p>Building <a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a> Phase 1, finalising water testing protocols, designing the <a href="/water-in-schools/">schools programme</a>, and seeking founding partners and grant funding.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="timeline-year">2027 &amp; Beyond</div>
            <h4>Scaling Honestly</h4>
            <p>Once Phase 1 has measurable, verified impact in Nairobi, we expand carefully. Vision: reach across East Africa &mdash; built on proof, not promises.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-title">Join Us in Our Mission</div>
    <p>Whether as a partner, volunteer, or supporter — there's a place for you at MiMaji Foundation. Together, we can make clean water accessible to every community.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/take-action/" class="btn btn-white">Take Action &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/programs/" class="btn btn-outline">View Programs</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .origin-image,
  .ecosystem-image {
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.12);
  }

  .origin-image img,
  .ecosystem-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .ecosystem-image {
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .about-text a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.08);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .value-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ecosystem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .eco-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .eco-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.1);
  }

  .eco-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--blue-light);
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .eco-badge.foundation {
    background: rgba(26, 158, 143, 0.1);
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .eco-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .eco-card h3 a {
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .eco-card h3 a:hover {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .eco-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid,
    .ecosystem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-values {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-values {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 7px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 0.3rem;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 3px solid var(--white);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-item.completed .timeline-marker {
    background: var(--teal);
  }

  .timeline-item.active .timeline-marker {
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(244, 169, 48, 0.2);
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .timeline-content a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
